"見住身邊啲人開始feel comfort以為高枕無憂就好撚心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推叫醒啲人啊唔該"},{"pid":"6ea11f0d43ce9f0a255b729aa2df53b162f653cb","tid":1756781,"uid":102420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4685fb6fdc865b851aaa3d9fb66d27e9135834d","tid":1756781,"uid":102420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a907462c13030362493f18c915c0e8e5306e18ef","tid":1756781,"uid":102420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a083223d36b7f67905737f337bb6abe17b4dc47","tid":1756781,"uid":102420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BshiMtq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBshiMtq.jpg&h=5161aa42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2afad1ae264a295f55613d73d68a58217b9d9989","tid":1756781,"uid":195334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"叫醒身邊既人啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25a50f80ad2226fbcb621cb94f40b43fb10fb19","tid":1756781,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf51b63ac5919a0b07833d1f6fd496cc30eaf63","tid":1756781,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"但諗深一層出來勇武抗爭其實都係制度內抗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為結局點勇武抗爭都係要subject to the laws<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ddbfe7d513f71c73dde7bff696a4e7b193caec","tid":1756781,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"今次區選除左當係民意授權之外根本冇撚用<br />\n事實證明好多人撐我地，但唔代表我地有實際成果<br />\n你想要既結果係泛民贏，定係想要民主同普選。<br />\n<br />\n仲推個啲咩立法會點先唔輸個啲 我屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7.1 衝立法會個一刻 唔係已經豁左出去 宣布議會既不合法性喇咩？當日就已經證明香港人既決心<br />\n我可以同你講 有功能組別 點選都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實啲諗，出年係可能都冇普選，但依家係咪冇更緊急既事可以做？定已經當抗爭完左？<br />\n<br />\n你要建制派輸，<br />\n只有一個方法：<br />\n繼續抗爭，直到有普選為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知每個人做到既野好少，但心態上要改變<br />\n停止打飛機，推行動Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都做到！<br />\n<br />\n制度內抗爭，香港人試左廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話咩雙軌並行一齊做（就算我比你拎六成直選，功能組別一樣輸到仆直）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係個句你想建制立法會輸 得一個方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續抗爭 直到有普選</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理遊行又好罷工又好裝修又有，真係唔想比人講中，選舉完抒發晒民怨就完，我地由此至始都冇獲得過啲咩，但損失左既係手足既命，佢地既前途。"},{"pid":"8328bf165f6b37722997074b8e2414d28e9cc5b7","tid":1756781,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8acf70a017d4fb06be9c6771673b4aa1993f5ae","tid":1756781,"uid":258128,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"我仲諗緊係咪自己疑心大<br />\n依家終於有人屌<br />\n見到出面個個post都帶緊風向重回左膠之路<br />\n心撚寒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"支線贏埋唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家明白係支線就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多後排唔敢衝個d 的無力感，比個出路比佢地都好呀<br />\n大家知道主力係前線抗爭，同時守住個後防<br />\n好似區議會咁，請返前線手足做職員，唔好比前線餓親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黃色經濟圈長遠都係，比手足有對前路的保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}